"P2257042543" "Fort Trident is in Atlas Park. Well, that is not entirely correct. The secret entrance to there is within Atlas Park. From there, you will be taken via submarine to the true location.<br><br>In Fort Trident, you can exchange <color yellow>Hero Merits you receive from reinforcing your alignment as a hero</color> for rare enhancements and recipes.<br><br>You can speak with a robot named BOTLER to learn more about this."
