"P3483707502" "Hello, {HeroName}! I am BOTLER, here at your service! Whenever you wish to trade in your Hero Merits, just come to me! Or rather, the device that is beside me. Simply insert the merits you have into this device and choose what you wish to receive! There's enough items in here to keep you occupied for a lifetime!"

